           If you like playing golf and are thinking of making a career of it, prodreamUSA is for you.  Founded by former Walker Cup winner and current professional golfer Lorne Kelly, prodreamUSA is run by three full time PGA Professionals all with US College experience.  prodreamUSA is Europe's most successful 'golf specific' placement service and is one of a kind. 
          
		  		Drawing on our unique profile and expertise we source, scout, educate and assess all eligible candidates and then promote them to recruiting US coaches.  As the first of our kind in the UK and Europe, we have established ourselves to be market leaders in US Golf Scholarship Industry.  We are proud to say we have a history that no other agency or placement service can match. prodreamusa prodream Golf Scholarship US USA UK GingerGolf amateur professional career
          
          
            
          
         
       
    	 
          	
       
       
       

         
   
	 
	 
	 
				 
	 
